Class EntityService

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.openadaptor.core.IComponent, org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor, org.openadaptor.core.jmx.Administrable, org.openadaptor.core.lifecycle.ILifecycleComponent
public class EntityService
extends org.openadaptor.core.lifecycle.LifecycleComponent
implements org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor

This component will find out whether an artifact coming out of the source system has to be created, updated, deleted or ignored within the target system. It will also try to find out the correct id of the artifact on the target system. It checks the version of the source artifact to see if that version of the artifact already shipped there by avoiding duplicate artifact shipment.

jnicolai

lookupTargetArtifactId

private java.lang.Object[] lookupTargetArtifactId(java.lang.String sourceArtifactId,
                                                  java.lang.String sourceSystemId,
                                                  java.lang.String sourceRepositoryId,
                                                  java.lang.String targetSystemId,
                                                  java.lang.String targetRepositoryId,
                                                  java.lang.String artifactType)
For a given source artifact id, source repository and the target repository details, this method finds out the target artifact id mapped to the source artifact id. If the source artifact id had ever passed through the wiring the identity mapping will contain the corresponding target artifact id. This method fetches the target artifact id and returns. If there is no target artifact id mapped to this source artifact id this method return a null.

Parameters:
sourceArtifactId - - The source artifact id that should be looked up for a target artifact id
sourceSystemId - - The system id of the source repository
sourceRepositoryId - - The repository id of the source artifact
targetSystemId - - The system id of the target repository
targetRepositoryId - - The repository id of the target artifact
artifactType - - The artifact type
Returns:
the target artifact id for the source artifact id
